Text:
Forecast for the rest of Sunday - Melbourne (where the race is on later today)

Summary
    Max 23
    Partly cloudy.
    Chance of any rain: 10%
    Rainfall amount: 0 to 0.2 mm

Melbourne area

Isolated light showers possible during the morning, then a mostly sunny afternoon. Winds south to southeasterly averaging up to 25 km/h tending east to southeasterly up to 20 km/h later in the evening.

BBC coverage much better than SKY.
Waiting for the race highlights.
Tank You
